highlights.text: Main Khiladi - From "Selfiee" by Tanishk Bagchi, Anu Malik, and Abhijeet is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Pune, up 39 spots at #32.
Maan Meri Jaan by King has been on Top Songs Pune the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Pune. Kesariya is the highest at #3.
Kya Mujhe Pyar Hai (From "Woh Lamhe") by KK is the highest new entry on Top Songs Pune at #80.
